    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >攻略提示：我已为您提供一份简要攻略以供不时之需，您可以在Steam客户端本游戏的右侧列表的“额外内容”中点击“手册”即可下载。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简介</h2>《山鬼》是一部第一人称，以战斗系统和支线探索为核心的生存恐怖游戏，使用<strong>CryEngine</strong>引擎打造。您可以通过远程与近战，物理与法术等不同类型的战斗风格，反击各种主线与支线故事中独特的敌人。同时体验主角被迫与自己那早已被扭曲的命运抗争，在这片饕餮盛宴的残渣中挣扎的过程，并为其书写各种结局。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/a7b7c8624f86ab84e04a41aa41d4abd1.poster.avif?t=1650633446\" width=598 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/a7b7c8624f86ab84e04a41aa41d4abd1.webm?t=1650633446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/a7b7c8624f86ab84e04a41aa41d4abd1.mp4?t=1650633446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的敌人</h2>游戏中会遇到许多独特的敌人，它们拥有不同的行为模式和能力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/710b570a1638fb71a293a8ce087df764.poster.avif?t=1650633446\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/710b570a1638fb71a293a8ce087df764.webm?t=1650633446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/710b570a1638fb71a293a8ce087df764.mp4?t=1650633446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样的武器与道具</h2>你可以通过探索或者击败敌人得到许多近战武器、投掷物以及远程法术等，这些道具拥有不同的攻击方式与伤害类型。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/c1fb7f5326915263bb22e705926d8af2.poster.avif?t=1650633446\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/c1fb7f5326915263bb22e705926d8af2.webm?t=1650633446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/c1fb7f5326915263bb22e705926d8af2.mp4?t=1650633446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >非线性探索</h2>大多数敌人都是可选或者需要触发的，同时一些支线故事会影响到最后的结局。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/81097a111994a8e0d645083454ecb784.poster.avif?t=1650633446\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/81097a111994a8e0d645083454ecb784.webm?t=1650633446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/81097a111994a8e0d645083454ecb784.mp4?t=1650633446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >灵活的难度等级</h2>支线故事中的可选谜题与敌人整体来说更难一些，同时你可能没有足够的资源轻松地与所有敌人战斗，这种难度控制方式更加灵活且能够提供不同的游戏体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/fbf7833edcc7fedc372286ae16143679.poster.avif?t=1650633446\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/fbf7833edcc7fedc372286ae16143679.webm?t=1650633446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1265650/extras/fbf7833edcc7fedc372286ae16143679.mp4?t=1650633446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
